# Line-ending policy: LF in the repository and the working tree for text
# files, so cross-repo byte-identity checks (shared db.py copies) hold on
# every checkout and Git stops emitting CRLF conversion warnings.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.xlsx binary
*.xls binary
*.zip binary
*.duckdb binary
*.parquet binary
*.dta binary